<style 
      xmlns="http://purl.org/net/xbiblio/csl"
      class="note"
      version="1.0">
  <info>
    <id />
    <title />
    <updated>2009-08-10T04:49:00+09:00</updated>
  </info>
  <macro name="shortdate">
      <date variable="issued" delimiter="-">
        <date-part name="year"/>
        <date-part name="month" form="numeric"/>
      </date>
  </macro>
  <macro name="longdate">
      <date variable="issued" delimiter="-">
        <date-part name="year"/>
        <date-part name="month" form="numeric"/>
        <date-part name="day" form="numeric"/>
      </date>
  </macro>
  <citation>
    <sort>
      <key macro="shortdate"/>
      <key variable="title"/>
    </sort>
    <layout delimiter=", ">
      <group delimiter=" ">
        <text variable="title"/>
        <text macro="longdate" prefix="(" suffix=")"/>
      </group>
    </layout>
  </citation>
</style>
